---
title: Quick Chilli Jam-Glazed Pork & Avocado Salad with Carrot Couscous & Balsamic Dressing
description: Zingy, sweet and packed with umami, our chilli jam is the perfect glaze for tender pork loin steaks. Freshen the dish up with a sharp
and creamy avocado-rocket salad, drizzled with balsamic dressing and you're on your way to an unforgettable fusion dinner!
